title: The last full moon of winter will illuminate the sky this week
description: Here's when to catch the worm moon, the last full moon of this winter season.

title: US imposes visa sanction on Syrian military official over massacre that killed at least 41 unarmed civilians
description: The US State Department on Monday imposed a visa sanction on a Syrian military official whom it says killed at least 41 unarmed civilians in a neighborhood of Damascus in April 2013.

title: Medics, teacher, parents accuse Iran government of silencing victims of suspected poisoning attacks
description: Iran has experienced a spike in suspected poisoning attacks at girls' schools across the country in recent days, according to state and semi-official media, as medical staff and teachers accused government officials of attempting to silence the victims.
